[img]http://i921.photobucket.com/albums/ad56/XTCBunny/Ultimate%20PvP/New.jpg[/img] [img]http://i921.photobucket.com/albums/ad56/XTCBunny/Ultimate%20PvP/2vumy4x.png[/img]
[i][b]Very good server for hybriding, ( Perfect magic, instant switches, great combat.) Perfect magic, ( instant freezing, perfect freezing timers, all gfx, spell build ups.)[/b][/i]
[i][b]There are alot of ways to make money, Here are a few: Killing KBD Killing Chaos Elemental Pk for items, and pk points to buy items Theive (First stall 1m, Second stall 2m, third stall 3m, fourth stall 5m) [/b][/i]
Great Combat - this is the real deal. We don’t have choppy, slow, combat like the servers out there that are based off DeltaScape. Before you try to criticize it isn’t perfect, log in and experience it. You’ll be amazed by how smooth it is and you might even feel like you’re playing RS when it was still considered decent. Hell, I wouldn’t be surprised at all. Loads of Bosses: Sea Troll Queen, God War Bosses, King Black Dragon, Chaos Elemental, Dagannoths. Unlike most servers, we’ve made the bosses extremly realistic. The dagannoths is a exact replica of how RS has it. To show proof of that, view the the pictures of it below. Excellent Minigames: Pest Control, Barrows, Duel Arena, Fight Pits, and more. I don’t like to repeat myself but I’ve to say this: perfection. Clan Chat and LootShare: It’s really basic but I’ve to say it’s 5x more advance then what any server has managed to make. Compared to the real DeltaScape, our clan chat and lootshare system makes theirs look like complete shit.
